== 古生态学 ==
巴利沃纳猎龙来自于{{link-en|莫雷利亚组|Arcillas de Morella Formation}}，该地层可追溯到1.294亿至1.25亿年前的[[白垩纪|早白垩世]][[巴列姆阶|巴列姆阶]]。<ref name=":0" />此生态环境中与它共存的恐龙包括[[鸟臀目|鸟臀目]]的[[禽龙属|贝尼萨特禽龙]]和[[莫雷利亚齿龙属|贝氏莫雷利亚齿龙]]、一种不确定的[[蜥脚类|蜥脚类]]以及一种不确定的重爪龙亚科。<ref name="cretaceousdistribution">Weishampel, David B; et al. (2004). "Dinosaur distribution (Early Cretaceous, Europe)." In: Weishampel, David B.; Dodson, Peter; and Osmólska, Halszka (eds.): The Dinosauria, 2nd, Berkeley: University of California Press. Pp. 562. {{ISBN|0-520-24209-2}}.</ref><ref name="indvar">{{cite journal|last1=Verdú|first1=F.J.|last2=Godefroit|first2=P.|last3=Royo-Torres|first3=R.|last4=Cobos|first4=A.|last5=Alcalá|first5=L.|date=2017|title=Individual variation in the postcranial skeleton of the Early Cretaceous ''Iguanodon bernissartensis'' (Dinosauria: Ornithopoda)|journal=Cretaceous Research|volume=74|pages=65–86|doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2017.02.006}}</ref>

